{"tid":2037214,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"突發！中午和你LUNCH","createTime":"2020-05-27T00:59:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T01:43:55.000Z","uid":270034,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"791e4c5e09930a07d7c58031ba8ca049efb9eb6a","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T00:59:41.000Z","msg":"唔好帶裝啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nSUCK CHANNEL <br />\n突發  5.27 反國法遊行<br />\n<br />\n集合地點分別為 : <br />\n中環-畢打街  <br />\n銅鑼灣-軒尼詩道 <br />\n<br />\n時間 : 1300<br />\n<br />\n裝備 : 迷彩  , 空身   <br />\n<br />\n戰術 : <br />\n-利用中午Lunch hour 時份 <br />\n-混合不同陣型於身份人仕於繁華鬧市地點集合行動<br />\n-港島 &quot;蜘蛛網&quot; 弱點係無法於每條街應對大量人流<br />\n-多於一地點集合避免一網打盡<br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n注意事項<br />\n<br />\n⚠️提早制定撤退時間表<br />\n<br />\n⚠️本次行動為無不反遊行  請現場集合夠一定人數後開始起行<br />\n<br />\n⚠️詳細情況請按個人情況修改  <br />\n<br />\n⚠️本頻會按現況隨時更新有關本次召集地點<br />\n<br />\n希望share出去<br />\n有連登account既開開po<br />\n估計可能為本日最後一次成功既召集<br />\n<br />\n一一一一一一一一一一一<br />\n實有人問 <br />\n都阻唔到通過又開到會點解仲要做?<br />\n<br />\n如果今日唔出黎 <br />\n柒婆咪大條道理同國際講<br />\n嗱 你班香港人都支持通過 <br />\n無人出黎反抗我地開會即係支持國法啦<br />\n<br />\n我地係會支持呢條國法通過咩?  <br />\n一直講實際行動好重要<br />\n<br />\n就算要國際為我地發聲  都要本地有人企出黎話 <br />\n我反對 !!  咁先會有人幫我地撐頭<br />\n試問如果連本地居民都唔出聲 <br />\n邊個幫到你?<br />\n<br />\n柒婆 : 好高興見到好多香港市民今日返工 , 多謝支持國安法"},{"pid":"c21d15af4e28958b62ec758de6c20245e0471e35","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:00:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"541095b3081deb22ce7cdfdc0fac9ddcb7cafc76","tid":2037214,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:00:33.000Z","msg":"推呢個<br />\n起碼有共識容易聚人<br />\n<br />\n唔好講咩啲狗都知， <br />\n啲狗知唔知都拉人，<br />\n點解我地唔聚多啲人"},{"pid":"e292b7f448df3c7250414ff3fbd860dc7bd210f5","tid":2037214,"uid":89349,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:00:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/peT8V93.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpeT8V93.png&h=419e79fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警務人員子女關注組<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1870807\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1870807</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"b37394ddd76b3cc2de15520e927e0452284dda35","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:00:37.000Z","msg":"香"},{"pid":"67e2011e471fa221164531e4b5b2bb4c8d373cca","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:00:48.000Z","msg":"港"},{"pid":"b0e6e3067a0a898114ea6c214593b84d69d72fe0","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:00:58.000Z","msg":"獨"},{"pid":"429b087cafdfdeae6e60d0d1ddbfefbd463a5b04","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-27T01:01:08.000Z","msg":"立"},{"pid":"d9aac2566803e26689bb9235e4ae1ff260abf5bc","tid":2037214,"uid":270034,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi